96 manager appointed by the board, and each departmental manager
97 appointed by the general manager, now or hereafter serving as
98 such, shall be indemnified by the board against any and all
99 claims and liabilities to which he or she has or shall become
100 subject by reason of serving or having served as such or by
101 reason of any action alleged to have been taken, omitted, or
102 neglected by him or her as such board member or manager; and
103 the board shall reimburse each such person individual for all
104 legal expenses reasonably incurred by him or her in connection
105 with any such claim or liability, provided, however, that no
106 such person individual shall be indemnified against, or be
107 reimbursed for, any expense incurred in connection with any
108 claim or liability arising out of his or her own willful
109 misconduct or gross negligence.
